      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing and driving as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. Every aspect of the car, from the flawless paint and pristine interior to the meticulously maintained engine, is in perfect order. It has been kept in a climate-controlled environment and has no signs of wear or mechanical issues. This is a rare find for a buyer seeking a car in showroom-perfect state.",
